description: This file contains unit tests for a queue implementation using Google Test framework, focusing on class QueueType with operations like Insert, Post, Remove, Extract, Enable, Disable, and Flush.

classes.name: QueueType
classes.description: A template class representing a queue, used in the unit test to verify its functionality.

methods.name: Insert
methods.description: Inserts an item with a priority or parameter into the queue.

methods.name: Post
methods.description: Posts or signals the queue with an item or event.

methods.name: Remove
methods.description: Removes an item from the queue.

methods.name: Extract
methods.description: Extracts an item from the queue, possibly with a priority parameter.

methods.name: Length
methods.description: Returns the current number of items in the queue.

methods.name: Flush
methods.description: Clears all items from the queue.
